entry.value: update log_summary as b set processed_records= a.processed_records from ( select ff_uuid,(sum(total_records)-sum(blank_lines+duplicate_records+datatype_mismatch)-sum(id+exam_id+semester+exam_code+student_uid+school_id+studying_class+question_id+obtained_marks+grade+subject_id))as processed_records from log_summary where filename like 'semester_exam%' group by ff_uuid) as a where a.ff_uuid=b.ff_uuid
